{/* SECTIE 8 - VEELGESTELDE VRAGEN */}
<section id="faq" class="py-24 md:py-32 px-6 lg:px-8 bg-white md:pt-48 fade-in-section">
	<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
		<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-semibold mb-12 md:mb-16 text-center">Veelgestelde Vragen</h2>
		
		<div class="space-y-6 md:space-y-8">
			<details class="group bg-[var(--color-brand-base)] rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm shadow-[var(--color-brand-muted)]/5 open:bg-white open:ring-1 open:ring-[var(--color-brand-secondary)] transition-colors duration-300">
				<summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-semibold cursor-pointer list-none p-6 md:p-8 text-lg md:text-xl">
					<span class="pr-6">Is dit een vervanging voor medische zorg?</span>
					<span class="transition-transform duration-500 ease-in-out group-open:rotate-180 shrink-0">
						<svg fill="none" height="24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9" /></svg>
					</span>
				</summary>
				<div class="faq-content text-[var(--color-brand-muted)] px-6 md:px-8 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
					<div class="pb-6 md:pb-8">
						<p>Nee. Ik werk altijd naast de reguliere zorg, nooit ertegen. Ik adviseer nooit om behandelingen te stoppen of medicatie af te bouwen. Wat ik bied is aanvullend: inzicht in de biologische processen achter je klachten, en begeleiding bij het verwerken van de onderliggende conflicten.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</details>
			
			<details class="group bg-[var(--color-brand-base)] rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm shadow-[var(--color-brand-muted)]/5 open:bg-white open:ring-1 open:ring-[var(--color-brand-secondary)] transition-colors duration-300">
				<summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-semibold cursor-pointer list-none p-6 md:p-8 text-lg md:text-xl">
					<span class="pr-6">Is dit wetenschappelijk bewezen?</span>
					<span class="transition-transform duration-500 ease-in-out group-open:rotate-180 shrink-0">
						<svg fill="none" height="24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9" /></svg>
					</span>
				</summary>
				<div class="faq-content text-[var(--color-brand-muted)] px-6 md:px-8 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
					<div class="pb-6 md:pb-8">
						<p>De biologische natuurwetten zijn een framework gebaseerd op klinische observaties, geen door gerandomiseerde studies bewezen methode. Wat ik je kan vertellen is dat ik in meer dan tien jaar dagelijks met dit kader werk, en dat de systematiek keer op keer klopt. Veel mensen ervaren voor het eerst begrip voor wat er in hun lichaam gebeurt â€” en dat begrip is op zichzelf al waardevol.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</details>

			<details class="group bg-[var(--color-brand-base)] rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm shadow-[var(--color-brand-muted)]/5 open:bg-white open:ring-1 open:ring-[var(--color-brand-secondary)] transition-colors duration-300">
				<summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-semibold cursor-pointer list-none p-6 md:p-8 text-lg md:text-xl">
					<span class="pr-6">Ik heb nog nooit van GNM gehoord. Is dit traject geschikt?</span>
					<span class="transition-transform duration-500 ease-in-out group-open:rotate-180 shrink-0">
						<svg fill="none" height="24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9" /></svg>
					</span>
				</summary>
				<div class="faq-content text-[var(--color-brand-muted)] px-6 md:px-8 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
					<div class="pb-6 md:pb-8">
						<p>Ja. Ik leg je tijdens het traject alles uit wat je nodig hebt. Je hoeft geen voorkennis te hebben. Wat je nodig hebt is de bereidheid om op een andere manier naar je klachten te kijken.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</details>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	/* CSS Grid Height Tweening Animation for Details/Summary */
	details > summary {
		list-style: none; /* Hide standard arrow */
	}
	details > summary::-webkit-details-marker {
		display: none;
	}
	
	.faq-content {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-rows: 0fr;
		opacity: 0;
		transition: grid-template-rows 400ms ease-in-out, opacity 400ms ease-in-out;
		will-change: grid-template-rows, opacity;
	}
	
	.faq-content > div {
		overflow: hidden;
	}
	
	details[open] .faq-content {
		grid-template-rows: 1fr;
		opacity: 1;
	}
</style>

<script>
	document.addEventListener('astro:page-load', () => {
		// FAQ Smooth specific fix: Prevent default details jump, use animation instead
		const detailsElements = document.querySelectorAll('details');
		detailsElements.forEach((targetDetail) => {
			targetDetail.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
				// We only want to intercept clicks on the summary element
				if (e.target.tagName !== 'SUMMARY' && !e.target.closest('summary')) return;
				
				e.preventDefault();
				
				if (targetDetail.hasAttribute('open')) {
					// Close animation
					targetDetail.classList.remove('is-open'); // Hook for custom states if needed
					targetDetail.querySelector('.faq-content').style.opacity = '0';
					targetDetail.querySelector('.faq-content').style.gridTemplateRows = '0fr';
					
					// Wait for CSS transition to finish before actually removing the open attribute
					setTimeout(() => {
						targetDetail.removeAttribute('open');
					}, 400); // matches the 400ms transition duration
				} else {
					// Open animation
					// Close others first (accordion style)
					detailsElements.forEach(detail => {
						if(detail !== targetDetail && detail.hasAttribute('open')) {
							detail.querySelector('.faq-content').style.opacity = '0';
							detail.querySelector('.faq-content').style.gridTemplateRows = '0fr';
							setTimeout(() => {
								detail.removeAttribute('open');
							}, 400);
						}
					});

					targetDetail.setAttribute('open', '');
					targetDetail.classList.add('is-open');
					
					// Small trick: force a reflow before animating to '1fr' to ensure transition runs
					const content = targetDetail.querySelector('.faq-content');
					content.getBoundingClientRect(); 
					
					// Trigger opening transitions
					content.style.opacity = '1';
					content.style.gridTemplateRows = '1fr';
				}
			});
		});
	});
</script>
